Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.44,0:00:05.24,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,After I got separated \N from Roy and Dot on Mt. Nappé,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.24,0:00:07.86,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I found myself face-to-face \N with Amethio from the Explorers.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.74,0:00:11.32,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Spinel also showed up \N in the middle of our battle...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.32,0:00:14.29,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,and used a strange stone \N that did {\i1}something{\i0} to his Blacky!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.29,0:00:21.58,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Terapagos managed to calm things down, \N but I wound up trapped in a cave with Amethio!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.26,0:00:32.39,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Terapagos!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.60,0:00:40.27,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,I’m not planning anything now.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.27,0:00:41.40,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.79,0:01:05.17,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh? Just like that...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.55,0:01:10.26,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Seems it understood \N that I mean it no harm.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.82,0:01:31.90,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.49,0:01:36.28,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Roy, Dot... \N I’m making you worry about me again...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.37,0:01:45.25,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Of all times, why now?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.25,0:01:46.88,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Shove off! We’re in a hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.84,0:01:50.09,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.09,0:01:51.88,Main,Onyx,0,0,0,,You’ll have to {\i1}make{\i0} us leave.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.38,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.38,0:01:55.01,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Calm down, Roy.
Comment: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:01.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:31.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.41,0:03:47.87,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,We don’t have time \N to deal with them.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.87,0:03:48.83,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.83,0:03:50.17,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Let’s all make a break for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.25,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Hogator, dash!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.84,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Welcamo, run for it too!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.67,0:03:56.63,Main,Onyx,0,0,0,,Kyojiohn! Stone Edge!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.76,0:04:06.06,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Whoa there! \N Whatcha runnin’ away for?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.06,0:04:07.64,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Think we’d make it that easy?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.64,0:04:10.23,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Onigohri! Blizzard!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.32,0:04:16.28,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Hogator!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.28,0:04:17.57,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Welcamo!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.57,0:04:20.82,Main,Onyx,0,0,0,,Use Salt Pickling!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.20,0:04:24.99,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Oh no! Dodge it, Welcamo!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.25,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Hogator!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.92,0:04:32.21,Main,Onyx,0,0,0,,So, one of them \N managed to slip away from me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.04,Main,Onyx,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.04,0:04:35.38,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Onigohri! Ice Spinner!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.59,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.59,0:04:42.89,Main,Onyx,0,0,0,,Show a bit more restraint.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.89,0:04:44.97,Main,Onyx,0,0,0,,There’s no gain \N in defeating them right away.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.97,0:04:48.77,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Stalling for time \N just ain’t Sango’s style!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.77,0:04:50.65,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Stalling for time?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.65,0:04:53.36,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,They’re deliberately \N trying to slow us down?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.36,0:04:55.53,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Which means... \N They’re after Liko!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.19,0:04:59.11,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,That’s bad! We’ve gotta move!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.36,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Roy. Let’s work together.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.36,0:05:02.20,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.66,0:05:05.20,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,We’ll take them down,\N starting with Kyojiohn.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.20,0:05:06.95,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.91,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,We’ll exploit the Rock type’s weaknesses.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.75,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Gotcha. So...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.92,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Hogator! Stomping Tantrum!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.92,0:05:20.84,Main,Onyx,0,0,0,,Kyojiohn! Crush it with Stone Edge!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.39,0:05:27.52,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Now, Welcamo! Aqua Break!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.27,0:05:32.44,Main,Roy and Dot,0,0,0,,It landed!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.36,0:05:38.15,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Now, stand back and let us—{(us through)}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.15,0:05:39.32,Main,Onyx,0,0,0,,Kyojiohn!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.32,0:05:40.32,Main,Onyx,0,0,0,,Self-Regenerate!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.78,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,It healed...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.78,0:05:48.08,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,...the damage?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.71,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Always makes for \N a nasty li’l surprise.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.71,0:05:54.33,Main,Onyx,0,0,0,,Now we’re right back \N where we started. Bring it on!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.30,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Think, think!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.43,0:06:12.06,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It’s getting colder and colder.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.06,0:06:14.06,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,If we don’t do something soon...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.69,0:06:20.36,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,And I know Nyarote \N doesn’t like the cold, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.44,0:06:23.49,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh? Nyarote?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.96,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What? You want me to \N keep warm with this?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.21,0:06:37.75,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Thank you, Nyarote!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.60,0:06:48.85,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Soublades...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.14,0:06:53.52,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Thank you. That helps.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.52,0:06:58.40,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.90,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Let me have{use} this grass.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.86,0:07:07.70,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.33,0:07:11.87,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I have a request to make of Soublades.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.54,0:07:17.50,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,If you light this grass to make a fire, \N it’ll help keep all of us warm.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.59,0:07:25.84,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Soublades. Light it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.98,0:07:36.35,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Amazing! Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.98,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It’s so warm!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.94,0:07:45.86,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.12,0:07:55.66,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,During our battle earlier...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.54,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,I saw you hesitate.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.25,0:08:01.84,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,When faced with \N my Terastallized Soublades,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.84,0:08:03.25,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,why did you give in so easily?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.85,0:08:20.35,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I was taking a Terastal Course... \N But I ended up failing.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.61,0:08:23.77,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I thought all my hard work \N was paying off...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.77,0:08:25.65,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,But now it’s gone, \N out of my reach...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.24,0:08:29.74,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I thought that \N if I was able to use Terastal,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.74,0:08:33.99,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I could learn more about this little one, \N and do more to help it, too.{Dread Terapagos}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.99,0:08:36.70,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,So I was really hoping to pass...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.54,0:08:41.88,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Are you going to give up?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.00,0:08:49.63,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,{\q2}I ask you... Is hitting one stumbling block all it takes \N for you to give up and declare yourself worthless?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.18,0:08:58.60,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,No way! I’m not done yet...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.60,0:09:02.10,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,The search for the Six Heroes, \N the adventure to Rakua...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.69,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,They’re not over yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.15,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I’m not ready to give up!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.86,0:09:08.69,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.28,0:09:13.95,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I’ve been wanting to ask you...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.58,0:09:17.91,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Back in the battle with \N the black Rekkuuza...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.83,0:09:20.33,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Why did you save me?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.84,0:09:28.21,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,As I told you...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.21,0:09:29.72,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,I {\i1}wasn’t{\i0} saving you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.05,0:09:32.38,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,But you {\i1}did{\i0} save me!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.38,0:09:33.47,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I made it, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.26,0:09:35.85,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.35,0:09:41.44,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,The Explorers are evildoers \N pursuing Terapagos and the black Rekkuuza.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.44,0:09:44.81,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,But something feels different about you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.15,0:09:47.53,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.53,0:09:50.36,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Why do you need Terapagos \N and the black Rekkuuza?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.99,0:09:55.87,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,It is all for Gibeon-sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.70,0:09:57.87,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Gibeon?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.41,0:10:03.54,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,My grandfather, leader of the Explorers.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.17,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,He wants to reach Rakua.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.75,0:10:10.38,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Terapagos and the black Rekkuuza \N are beings that lead to Rakua.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.38,0:10:12.72,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,I want to fulfill my grandfather’s dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.89,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It’s... for your grandfather?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.81,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,I want to be more than just his grandson.{tagging in case this gets returned to way later... -ed}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.81,0:10:24.27,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,I want to live up to \N Gibeon-sama’s expectations!{Terapagos reacts to word Gibeon again}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.45,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Terapagos...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.45,0:10:41.20,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It’s okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.54,0:10:49.04,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I’m on an adventure I inherited \N from my grandma, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.75,0:10:55.38,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I want to reach Rakua, for Terapagos— \N the pendant my grandma gave me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.47,0:11:00.72,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It wants to go to Rakua, \N so I decided I’d take it there.{Dread Terapagos}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.35,0:11:03.68,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Terapagos itself wants to go to Rakua...?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.77,0:11:08.11,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,So maybe the two of us \N are following the same path.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.32,0:11:13.53,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I’m glad I asked.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.53,0:11:18.32,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,‘Til now, I’ve only ever thought of you \N as an enemy who was after Terapagos.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.12,0:11:21.79,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,I’ve only ever seen you...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.79,0:11:24.62,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,...as the girl with the Terapagos.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.21,0:11:27.33,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,I’d never even considered \N what your goal was.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.79,0:11:31.59,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Now I can see there’s stuff you’ll just never know \N if you don’t hear people out.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.13,0:11:33.42,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.06,0:11:43.56,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.77,0:11:46.56,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Let’s get out of here...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.23,0:11:48.19,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Liko!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.56,0:11:51.32,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Right!
Comment: 0,0:11:57.53,0:11:57.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part C}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.96,0:12:07.87,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Get out of here, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.59,0:12:12.50,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Look up.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.01,0:12:21.01,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,That grass is swaying because \N there’s a breeze coming through.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.43,0:12:23.31,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,I can also see a dim light.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.31,0:12:25.47,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,There’s a chance that it leads outside.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.47,0:12:27.06,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Meaning...!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.06,0:12:29.94,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Armorgaw can fly us up there.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.94,0:12:31.61,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,But I want to widen the opening a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.77,0:12:35.15,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote, help us out!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.61,0:12:40.20,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Go! Armorgaw!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.04,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Soublades, use Psycho Cutter!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.04,0:12:49.96,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote, use Magical Leaf!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.46,0:12:58.59,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Summon up all your strength, Soublades! \N Psycho Cutter!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.55,0:13:02.93,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote, give me \N a whole lot of Magical Leaves!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.60,0:13:09.35,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Get back!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.35,0:13:10.60,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Tebrim!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.27,0:13:14.52,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Mind Power!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.53,0:13:18.03,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Follow up with Brutal Swing!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.41,0:13:26.99,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Thank you, Tebrim!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.87,0:13:28.58,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.04,0:13:33.42,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Hogator!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.83,0:13:36.42,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,C’mon! That all you got?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.30,0:13:39.17,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,What now? The way this is going...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.17,0:13:42.18,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,This is a total drag! \N They’ve got zero fight in ‘em!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.18,0:13:44.01,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Guess it’s time I wrap this up!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.01,0:13:47.51,Main,Onyx,0,0,0,,Don’t forget! \N Our goal is to slow them down!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.51,0:13:50.06,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,But I’m so bored!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.06,0:13:52.44,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,About time for me to spice things up!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.94,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Onigohri!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.44,0:13:56.82,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Self-Destr—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.82,0:13:58.32,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Moonforce!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.69,0:14:02.36,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Onigohri!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.36,0:14:02.95,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Who did that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.95,0:14:06.83,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Grusha-san?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.83,0:14:07.58,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.58,0:14:09.08,Main,Onyx,0,0,0,,A Gym Leader?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.12,0:14:12.29,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,That is one frigid game you’re playing.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.13,0:14:25.34,Main,Onyx,0,0,0,,He’s good.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.34,0:14:27.10,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Well ain’t that somethin’?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.10,0:14:28.76,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Onigohri! Get up!
Comment: 10,0:14:32.77,0:14:35.52,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,Roto-Roto-Roto. \N Roto-Roto-Roto.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.11,Main,Agate,0,0,0,,Pull out.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.11,0:14:37.77,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.40,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Don’t you {\i1}dare{\i0} boss me around!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.07,0:14:42.11,Main,Agate,0,0,0,,We’ve achieved our objective.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.11,0:14:45.16,Main,Agate,0,0,0,,Battling a Gym Leader \N would hardly be wise.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.74,0:14:46.74,Main,Onyx,0,0,0,,We’re leaving.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.16,Main,Onyx,0,0,0,,Return, Kyojiohn.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.00,0:15:00.84,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Listen up, dorks!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.84,0:15:03.30,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Next time, it’ll be total carnage! \N You hear me?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.35,0:15:12.02,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Grusha-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.43,Main,Roy and Dot,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.44,0:15:18.48,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,You didn’t want to battle them, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.48,0:15:21.94,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,We lost track of Liko, and they stopped us \N when we went to look for her!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.69,0:15:24.61,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,I’ve heard all about Liko.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.61,0:15:27.20,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Some guy named Friede called the Gym.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.20,0:15:29.28,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Let’s hurry.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.28,0:15:30.33,Main,Roy and Dot,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.56,0:15:54.98,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,We made it out...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.10,0:15:58.48,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,As a warning...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.48,0:15:59.86,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Watch out for Spinel.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.36,0:16:02.77,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,He’s bound to lay another \N cowardly trap eventually.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.77,0:16:03.48,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.86,0:16:06.36,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,As for that “Eternal Blessing”...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.36,0:16:08.20,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,He’s plotting something.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.49,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.49,0:16:13.12,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,The Rising Voltteccers \N and the Explorers...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.12,0:16:17.25,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,They share the same goal \N of reaching Rakua, don’t they?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.00,0:16:19.00,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.50,0:16:24.46,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Then couldn’t we work together \N instead of fighting?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.46,0:16:25.34,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Not possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.34,0:16:26.01,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.63,0:16:30.22,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Our goals may be the same, \N but our paths are not.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.22,0:16:32.47,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,I will follow my own path.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.02,0:16:40.35,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,We better get going too, Nyarote!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.99,0:16:53.91,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.20,0:16:56.45,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,A mark in the snow...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.45,0:16:57.79,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,It’s been moved?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.79,0:17:01.79,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Then that means... \N Liko went past this rock?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.79,0:17:04.80,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I could’ve seen that \N if I had just looked closer!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.80,0:17:06.30,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,You can’t always just look ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.76,0:17:09.76,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,The ground beneath your feet \N is what’s important.{surprisingly not a game line}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.76,0:17:10.84,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Tyltalis!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.65,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,That was a shock...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.65,0:17:23.36,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.81,0:17:24.90,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Liko!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.90,0:17:26.15,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Roy! Dot!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.40,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Are you okay? \N I’m so glad to see you!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.41,0:17:35.03,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I’m sorry... \N And thank you! I’m okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.50,0:17:40.91,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Guess they don’t need \N our help after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.67,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,You’d better warm yourselves up.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.38,0:17:51.88,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.51,0:17:53.64,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Grusha-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.72,0:17:56.64,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Sorry for making you worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.64,0:17:59.27,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Well, all worked out in the end, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.90,0:18:06.57,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I may have failed \N my implementation test,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.57,0:18:08.48,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,but that’s not the only path \N I could take.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.48,0:18:10.53,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,There must be more paths!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.53,0:18:12.95,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,If I keep trying \N and never give up, I bet...!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.95,0:18:17.08,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,If those guys showed their faces, \N maybe they’re starting to ramp things up.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.16,0:18:19.08,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Liko...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.08,0:18:21.00,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,What did Spinel come out here to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.58,0:18:22.37,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.08,0:18:27.71,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,When he used this pink crystal thing \N on his Blacky, it went on a rampage...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.21,0:18:33.30,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Spinel called it the Eternal Blessing.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.30,0:18:35.72,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,So he has the Rakurium?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.72,0:18:36.80,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Rakurium?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.80,0:18:41.56,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,A mysterious substance \N they kept at a lab I used to work at.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.56,0:18:43.81,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,I never knew it could do that...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.44,0:18:47.27,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Blacky seemed to be in a lot of pain...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.81,0:18:52.19,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,But when Terapagos transformed \N and unleashed its power,{Dread Terapagos}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.19,0:18:55.82,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Blacky went back to normal \N and the crystal disappeared.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.95,0:18:58.45,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,What do we take from that?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.95,0:19:03.50,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Heh, guess you can’t exactly \N answer{tell} me...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.08,0:19:05.87,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.87,0:19:10.05,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Keep an eye out for more activity from them. \N I’ll head back and fill everyone in.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.05,0:19:11.05,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.05,0:19:14.34,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,We should head down the mountain \N and back to Orange Academy.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.34,0:19:15.18,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.18,0:19:17.22,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Hold on. Roy, Dot...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.05,0:19:20.39,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,There’s somewhere I want to go first!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.57,0:19:34.36,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,We made it! \N Paldea’s Highest Peak!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.41,0:19:41.74,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.33,0:19:45.71,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,We’re as high up as anyone can go...{We're in the highest spot.}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.71,0:19:48.00,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I’m glad we got to see this together.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.00,0:19:48.92,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.38,0:19:53.30,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,We’ve seen so many sights{keshiki} already,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.30,0:19:58.51,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,But every time... Every single time, \N it feels like we’re seeing the best one yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.51,0:19:59.89,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Liko!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.89,0:20:02.51,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Let’s take a photo!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.89,0:20:05.02,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Yeah! I’m coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.35,0:20:06.52,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.89,0:20:09.23,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Three, two, one...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.41,0:20:26.54,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Why did you call for me? \N What’s going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.42,0:20:30.58,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Spinel!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.58,0:20:31.63,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,I need to ask you—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.63,0:20:32.92,Main,Spinel,0,0,0,,It’s such a pity.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.55,0:20:36.67,Main,Spinel,0,0,0,,I never dreamed \N that you would betray us.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.09,0:20:38.18,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,What...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.84,0:20:42.55,Main,Hamber,0,0,0,,This is what Spinel-sama reported.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.56,0:20:51.31,Main,Agate,0,0,0,,What led you to collaborate with the enemy \N without even notifying us?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.86,0:20:55.15,Main,Spinel,0,0,0,,You even let Terapagos escape \N before your very eyes...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.15,0:20:56.65,Main,Spinel,0,0,0,,It’s beyond comprehension.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.07,0:20:59.07,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,So this was your plan all along, was it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.07,0:21:01.41,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,Hold it, Ame-pyon.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.41,0:21:03.58,Main,Sango,0,0,0,,If you’ve got an excuse, \N I’ll hear ya out.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.95,0:21:06.20,Main,Onyx,0,0,0,,I, too, have my suspicions about this.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.62,Main,Hamber,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.62,0:21:13.08,Main,Hamber,0,0,0,,May we ask for a complete explanation \N of the events from your perspective?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.84,0:21:16.09,Main,Gibeon,0,0,0,,There is no need.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.63,0:21:18.09,Main,Hamber,0,0,0,,Gibeon-sama...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.09,0:21:20.59,Main,Gibeon,0,0,0,,You disappoint me, Amethio.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.59,0:21:22.09,Main,Amethio,0,0,0,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.93,0:21:24.35,Main,Gibeon,0,0,0,,So you were the same...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.81,0:21:29.31,Main,Gibeon,0,0,0,,So you would \N stray from the path, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.98,0:21:31.44,Main,Gibeon,0,0,0,,Begone.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.44,0:21:33.31,Main,Gibeon,0,0,0,,I wish to see your face no longer.
Comment: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:45.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{Professor Friede's Pokémon Seminar A}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.20,0:21:47.33,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Friede here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.33,0:21:49.37,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,It’s time for my Pokémon Seminar!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.00,0:21:54.58,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Today, let’s take a look at \N the Humming Pokémon, Tyltalis.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.58,0:21:58.84,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,A Pokémon with fluffy wings \N that resemble cottony cumulus clouds.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.84,0:22:04.30,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,They love to do a certain thing, \N but do you know what that thing is?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.30,0:22:06.39,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,See the answer after the commercials!
Comment: 0,0:22:07.56,0:22:07.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:37.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{Professor Friede's Pokémon Seminar B}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:38.36,0:23:40.57,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Now, time to announce \N the correct answer!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.32,0:23:44.15,Main,Friede,0,0,220,,The answer is A: Sing!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.15,0:23:47.32,Main,Friede,0,0,220,,Tyltalis love to sing!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:47.32,0:23:51.91,Main,Friede,0,0,220,,They sing in a beautifully clear, \N enrapturing soprano voice!
Comment: 0,0:24:00.59,0:24:00.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.09,0:24:04.97,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I hear the final part of the Terastal Course \N is a battle tournament!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:04.97,0:24:07.59,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,All right! I can’t wait!{orig: I just can't wait!}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.59,0:24:09.80,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Are the course students \N gonna be battling each other?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.80,0:24:11.43,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Let’s all do our best!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:13.31,0:24:14.81,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,What’s wrong, Welcamo?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.81,0:24:19.15,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Huh?! Could that be... \N the Explorers?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.65,0:24:23.02,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,And so! To be continued next time \N on Pocket Monsters!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.02,0:24:26.40,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,System Breach! \N A Crisis at Orange Academy!!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:27.78,0:24:30.53,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,We’ve gotta do something!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,
