Dialogue: 11,0:02:03.85,0:02:07.23,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{=1047}{\blur0.6\fad(350,0)\1a&HFF&\t(305,350,\1a&H00&)}Together, we challenge, chasing the future
Dialogue: 11,0:02:07.23,0:02:08.23,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}(Let’s go!)
Dialogue: 11,0:02:08.23,0:02:10.90,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}We gather, let’s catch it, chasing tomorrow
Dialogue: 11,0:02:10.90,0:02:11.94,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}(Hey, let’s go!)
Dialogue: 11,0:02:11.94,0:02:15.37,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Never give up - Every time you fall, stand up
Dialogue: 11,0:02:15.37,0:02:17.49,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 11,0:02:17.49,0:02:18.99,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}(Take a step out, go!)
Dialogue: 11,0:02:18.99,0:02:19.79,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}(hey buddy)
Dialogue: 11,0:02:19.79,0:02:24.04,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Imagining, dreaming, with my friend (oh)
Dialogue: 11,0:02:24.04,0:02:26.83,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}The light ahead of us, so bright
Dialogue: 11,0:02:26.83,0:02:28.96,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Once it catches your eye
Dialogue: 11,0:02:28.96,0:02:31.13,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}The rest is easy, leave it to me
Dialogue: 11,0:02:31.13,0:02:34.97,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}You and I will add to our story (oh-oh)
Dialogue: 11,0:02:34.97,0:02:36.93,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Always a little bit more (We are)
Dialogue: 11,0:02:36.93,0:02:39.14,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Closer than yesterday (Best friends)
Dialogue: 11,0:02:39.14,0:02:43.27,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}I’m making my debut into a new world with you
Dialogue: 11,0:02:43.27,0:02:46.19,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}We’re the challengers
Dialogue: 11,0:02:46.19,0:02:50.69,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}It’s set into motion now, our fateful adventure
Dialogue: 11,0:02:50.69,0:02:54.28,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}We’re the challengers
Dialogue: 11,0:02:54.28,0:02:56.45,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Watch us, tell us...
Dialogue: 11,0:02:56.45,0:02:57.82,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}(hey buddy, let’s go)
Dialogue: 11,0:02:57.82,0:03:02.29,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}We are buddy-buddy-buddies, chasing piles of dreams
Dialogue: 11,0:03:02.29,0:03:04.37,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Wish it, and it’ll come true, you know it
Dialogue: 11,0:03:04.37,0:03:05.71,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Get over here, Challenger
Dialogue: 11,0:03:05.71,0:03:09.67,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Now, to chase spark-spark-sparkling bright tomorrows
Dialogue: 11,0:03:09.67,0:03:11.63,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Leap out into that vast sky
Dialogue: 11,0:03:11.63,0:03:14.42,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}You sparkling Challenger
Dialogue: 11,0:03:14.42,0:03:17.26,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}We’re the challengers
Dialogue: 11,0:03:17.26,0:03:22.14,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Hand in hand, flying up-up-up higher
Dialogue: 11,0:03:22.14,0:03:25.81,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}We’re the challengers
Dialogue: 11,0:03:25.81,0:03:27.56,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 11,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.11,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}(Take a step out, go!)
Dialogue: 11,0:03:29.11,0:03:31.90,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Let’s challenge
