Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.85,0:22:12.39,ED,,0,0,0,,{=1045}{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Journey with buddy! Leap out!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.39,0:22:13.40,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Turn up the heat!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.40,0:22:15.44,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Ride on! In peak form! Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.44,0:22:16.94,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Coolly say "Let me battle"
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.94,0:22:20.36,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}That mysterious power everyone has
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.36,0:22:23.45,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}I want it too, come look and listen with me
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.45,0:22:25.24,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Heart pounding at the display (display)
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.24,0:22:26.87,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Leap past it, runaway (Yeah)
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.87,0:22:31.41,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Action! Dodging and weaving every which way
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.41,0:22:34.96,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}The mystery in my pocket, it must be adventure
Dialogue: 10,0:22:34.96,0:22:38.71,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Soaking up sun and rain, that's how seeds sprout
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.71,0:22:40.63,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Gotta beat my yesterday 1,2,3,4!!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.63,0:22:43.34,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Even by the smallest margin (Trial & error)
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.34,0:22:45.64,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}It's a new personal best!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:45.64,0:22:47.35,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&\c&H2725F5&}Tel{\c&H000000&}ling a {\c&H2725F5&}r{\c&H000000&}e{\c&H2725F5&}a{\c&H000000&}l hero-to-{\c&H2725F5&}c{\c&H000000&}ome's {\c&H2725F5&}S{\c&H000000&}tory{lit. Story of [one who] can become a hero}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:47.35,0:22:49.22,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Look to the fu{\c&HFE21A3&}t{\c&H000000&}ure, som{\c&HFE21A3&}e{\c&H000000&}day I'{\c&HFE21A3&}l{\c&H000000&}l get t{\c&HFE21A3&}o {\c&H000000&}cla{\c&HFE21A3&}i{\c&H000000&}m {\c&HFE21A3&}V{\c&H000000&}ictory{lit. If you look to tomorrow, sooner or later [I] claim Victory}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.22,0:22:50.81,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Nice to meet you, to the beat y'all
Dialogue: 10,0:22:50.81,0:22:53.10,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}It's super promising!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:53.10,0:22:56.77,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}I'm all set to hone my skills until I'm satisfied
Dialogue: 10,0:22:56.77,0:22:58.90,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}(Ready, hop! Ready, jump!)
Dialogue: 10,0:22:58.90,0:23:01.23,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}And go! Head past the furthest reaches
Dialogue: 10,0:23:01.23,0:23:03.53,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Never bind myself with limits
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.53,0:23:06.82,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Just seek out my way, 'til I catch it for sure
Dialogue: 10,0:23:06.82,0:23:08.74,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}(Beyond!) Hope's at a perfect 100%
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.74,0:23:10.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}(Reload!) Keep trying, every time
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.49,0:23:12.20,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Again, again, again...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.20,0:23:14.29,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Hello, future!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.29,0:23:16.71,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Journey with buddy! Leap out!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.71,0:23:17.71,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Turn up the heat!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.71,0:23:19.50,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Ride on! In peak form! Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:19.50,0:23:21.46,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Coolly say "Let me battle"
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.60,0:23:31.01,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Aee aye (Hey! Hey! Hey! Hey!...)
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.01,0:23:32.06,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&H00&}Alright, stay tuned, come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.06,0:23:36.23,ED,,0,0,0,,{=1046}{\fad(0,520)\blur0.6\4a&H00&}See you again tomorrow!
